reasoning_output.task_understanding:
Inspect the most-recent torsion-snapshot artifact bundle (the failed round_03 torsion attempt referenced by the Planner) by running inspect_raw_artifact_bundle (parse-only; no new calculations). Discover available artifact bundles first to identify the exact bundle ID, then inspect raw files (stdout logs, per-snapshot output files, and dihedral metadata) to extract:
1) whether any per-snapshot S1 outputs exist despite "normal_termination_missing";
2) which dihedral ID/label and the angle grid actually used (0,15,...,90 if present);
3) the exact log context around "Error occured in dpotrf!" from stdout;
4) a concise minimal-parameter recommendation for a rerun (e.g., reduced state_window and/or reduced angle list) — provided as a diagnostic suggestion only, without launching a rerun.

